log_type_id_constraint.name: log_type_id_constraint
log_type_id_constraint.value:
(
        (type = 'USER' AND user_id IS NOT NULL)
        OR (type = 'GROUP' AND group_id IS NOT NULL)
        OR (type = 'EXPENSE' AND expense_id IS NOT NULL)
        OR (type = 'SETTLEMENT' AND settlement_id IS NOT NULL)
        OR (type = 'FRIEND_REQUEST' AND friend_request_id IS NOT NULL)
        OR (
          type NOT IN ('USER', 'GROUP', 'EXPENSE', 'SETTLEMENT', 'FRIEND_REQUEST')
        )
      )

provider_password_oauth_check.name: provider_password_oauth_check
provider_password_oauth_check.value: ((provider = 'CREDENTIALS' AND hashed_password IS NOT NULL) OR (provider != 'CREDENTIALS' AND oauth_id IS NOT NULL))
